    think='This is extremely puzzling. The login button simply doesn\'t respond 
to Maestro taps. Let me try using ADB directly to tap the button after Maestro f
ills the fields.\n\nActually, wait. I just realized something. Looking at the sc
reenshot very carefully, the countdown says `33 s`. The `获取验证码` button was 
